    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。すみれはいつも時間ぴったりだな",
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "実は子役時代に、時間は必ず守れって教えられたんです\nそう教わってから、遅刻はゼロなんですよ。えっへん",
      "startTime": 13,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "凄いな。俺も今日からすみれを見習うよ\nところで、折り入って相談があるって聞いたけど",
      "startTime": 22.4000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。実は……\n今お話しした、子役時代のお仕事に関係してるんです",
      "startTime": 28.9333347321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "無理だったらいいんです。私のわがままですし\nでも、もし可能性があるなら、私……",
      "startTime": 39.4666695913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……もう一度、役者のお仕事をやってみたいんです",
      "startTime": 46.5333352407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それって今まですみれが自分から断っていた仕事だよな\n今はアイドルで、もう役者じゃないからって",
      "startTime": 55.8666695913,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}